data.description: Home sale fell through due to no fault of the seller. Charming 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home with a 3 car garage on a corner lot in the highly sought after Eagle Park community in Nixa!  This lovely home was just built in 2020, it offers an open concept living room and kitchen complete with an oversized island as a centerpiece for entertaining!  The modern kitchen offers tons of cabinet space and a walk-in pantry.  Make your way over to the main living area which features a contemporary gas fireplace and shiplap mantle. The spacious master bathroom features a tile shower, walk-in closet, and access to the laundry room to make laundry a breeze!  The master bedroom includes a tray ceiling and windows looking out to the fully fenced back yard.  The covered rear porch simply adds to the enjoyment of this lovely home. Full irrigation system in front and back yard, too many additional features to list.  Don't miss this one before it's gone!
